Heat Wizard README
-------------------

Heat Wizard is a small program for the conversion of thermocouple voltages
to temperature and back. It comes with a graphical user interface (GUI)
and runs on Windows, Mac OS X and Linux.

Installation:

Windows:
Double click the installer.

Mac OS X:
Double click the diskimage. Move the application to whereever you like.
Heat Wizard can start from any location.

Linux:
You need Lazarus and gettext for building the application from the 
source tarball.
Build and install Heat Wizard as usual. Type:

  make
  make install

Have fun.
